title: 287: Bucky's Mock Draft 4.0, MTS Draft Press Conference
itunes:title: 287: Bucky's Mock Draft 4.0, MTS Draft Press Conference
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks dive into Bucky's fourth mock draft (1:26). Who is the first QB off the board? You might be surprised. The guys then field questions from beat writers from around the country during their yearly pre-draft press conference (8:20).
